"""Windows Win32 API + UI Automation handler — real desktop control.

v2.1.1:
  PS: keyboard VkKeyScanW resolver for letter/numeral keys
  PS: activate_window fix: GetWindowThreadProcessId returns tuple
  PS: mouse_down/up: None,None → don't move cursor
  PS: surrogate pairs for emoji (UTF-16 units)
  PS: key_down/key_up: VkKeyScan for char keys, keydown-only/keyup-only
"""

